<Layout title="About Summit Exteriors" description="Summit Exteriors is a local, family-owned roofing company operating in Rochester NY. We have over 50 years of combined roofing experience and guarantee best roofing work in Rochester" heading="The Best Roofing Work in Rochester New York" >
<div class="flex flex-col mt-12">
<div class="flex flex-col-reverse md:flex-row ">
  <div class="md:w-1/2 m-auto p-4 max-w-[500px]">
    <h1 class="text-6xl md:text-start text-center font-black mb-2">We Are Summit</h1>
    <p>Founded in 2019 our CEO Andrew Delaus set out to change the roofing industry in Rochester. By creating a roofing system with the highest quality materials, we are trying to move the industry away from cut-and-paste roofs. You can trust us as the experts in roofing and exteriors with over +100 years of experience combined with our talented team.
    </p>
  </div>
  <img src="/teamphoto.png" alt="Summit Exteriors Rochester Roof Install" class="md:w-1/2 md:h-auto h-[300px]">
</div>

